Winter Olympics 1992 --
   Games Stats:
   Ice Hockey
-- Ratio of goals scored to goals allowed by U.S. since
1956: 1.3 to 1.
                                                                                                       

   -- Velocity of a well-hit slap shot: 90 to 100 mph.
                                                                                                       

   -- Number of Swiss citizens who registered displeasure
with calls by pelting officials with snowballs during the
1948 match between Canada and Switzerland: 5,000.
                                                                                                       

